# DnD Companion — Frontend Components

İki katman: **`components/`** (domain-agnostik, yeniden kullanılabilir) ve **`features/`** (domain UI + küçük logic). Sayfa orchestration → `pages/` (`21-frontend-routes.mdc`).

Form alanları → `22-frontend-forms.mdc`; a11y → `25-frontend-a11y.mdc`.

## Klasör Sınırları

| Konum | İçerik | Örnek |
| --- | --- | --- |
| `components/ui/` | shadcn/ui primitives | `Button`, `Dialog`, `Tabs` |
| `components/` | App-wide composite | `Pagination`, `EmptyState`, `ImageUpload` |
| `features/<domain>/` | Domain bileşen | `CampaignCard`, `LiveFieldCard` |
| `features/<domain>/builder/` | Character builder tab'ları | `RaceClassTab` |
| `pages/` | Route container | `CampaignListPage` |

```typescript
// ✓ Doğru — feature domain logic
// features/campaigns/InviteLinkManager.tsx
export function InviteLinkManager({ campaignId, isOwner }: Props) {
  const [regenerate] = useRegenerateInviteMutation();
  if (!isOwner) return null;
  // ...
}

// ✗ Yanlış — domain logic generic components'ta
// components/ui/button.tsx içinde campaign invite
```

## shadcn/ui Kullanımı

Bileşenler copy-paste `components/ui/` — npm `@shadcn/*` monolith paketi yok. Tailwind + `cn()` utility.

Temel set: `Button`, `Input`, `Textarea`, `Select`, `Checkbox`, `Switch`, `Card`, `Dialog`, `Sheet`, `Tabs`, `Table`, `Badge`, `DropdownMenu`, `Command`, `Toast`, `Skeleton`, `Accordion`, `Tooltip`, `Form`.

```typescript
// ✓ Doğru — variant via cn + cva
<Button variant="destructive" size="sm" aria-label="Delete campaign">
  Delete
</Button>

// ✗ Yanlış — inline style veya custom CSS module her yerde
<button style={{ color: 'red' }}>Sil</button>
```

Kullanılmayan shadcn bileşeni import etme — bundle şişmesin.

## Paylaşılan Composite Bileşenler

| Bileşen | Rol |
| --- | --- |
| `Pagination` | Cursor tabanlı liste footer |
| `SearchInput` | Debounced 300ms arama |
| `FilterBar` | Homebrew/reference filtre chip'leri |
| `DataTable` | Admin listeleri (sıralama `aria-sort`) |
| `EmptyState` | Liste boş + CTA |
| `LoadingSpinner` | `role="status"`, `aria-label="Loading"` |
| `ConfirmDialog` | Destructive action onay |
| `ImageUpload` | Resize + presign akışı |
| `EmailVerificationBanner` | Layout üstü sarı banner |

Props interface export et; `any` prop yasak.

## Feature: Campaign

- `CampaignCard` — liste kartı, hover prefetch opsiyonel.
- `MemberList` — üye avatar + username (email **gösterme** — PII).
- `InviteLinkManager` — DM-only; copy + regenerate.

## Feature: Character

- `CharacterSheet` — responsive grid/accordion.
- `CharacterCard` — liste özet.
- `LiveFieldsBadge` — WS bağlı göstergesi.
- `builder/*Tab` — builder tab içerikleri (`22-frontend-forms.mdc`).

### Character Sheet Responsive

```tsx
// ✓ Doğru — lg grid, mobil accordion
<div className="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 lg:grid-cols-3">
  <section className="lg:col-span-1">{/* abilities, HP, AC */}</section>
  <section className="lg:col-span-1">{/* skills, features */}</section>
  <section className="lg:col-span-1">{/* equipment, spells */}</section>
</div>
{/* mobil: Accordion ile aynı bölümler */}

// ✗ Yanlış — sabit 3 kolon tüm breakpoint'lerde
<div className="grid grid-cols-3">
```

## Feature: DM Screen (S-DM-SCREEN)

Masaüstü 2 kolon; mobil tab — **kritik layout**:

```tsx
// ✓ Doğru — lg split, mobil Tabs
function DmScreenPage() {
  useWebSocket(campaignId);
  return (
    <>
      <div className="hidden lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-6">
        <PlayerCharacterPanel campaignId={campaignId} />
        <DmNotesPanel campaignId={campaignId} />
      </div>
      <div className="lg:hidden">
        <Tabs defaultValue="players">
          <TabsList aria-label="DM Screen sections">
            <TabsTrigger value="players">Players</TabsTrigger>
            <TabsTrigger value="notes">Notes</TabsTrigger>
          </TabsList>
          <TabsContent value="players">
            <PlayerCharacterPanel campaignId={campaignId} />
          </TabsContent>
          <TabsContent value="notes">
            <DmNotesPanel campaignId={campaignId} />
          </TabsContent>
        </Tabs>
      </div>
    </>
  );
}

// ✗ Yanlış — mobilde 2 kolon squeeze
<div className="grid grid-cols-2">
```

`PlayerCharacterPanel`: live field kartları (`LiveFieldCard` — HP, conditions, death saves). `DmNotesPanel`: not listesi + inline edit.

Full-width layout — App sidebar gizli (`21-frontend-routes.mdc`).

## Feature: Homebrew

- `HomebrewCard` — galeri kartı, `aspect-ratio` CLS önleme.
- `HomebrewForm` — type conditional (`22-frontend-forms.mdc`).
- `StatusBadge` — DRAFT/PUBLISHED renk + metin (renk tek başına anlam taşımaz).

Galeri: `lg` 3–4 kolon grid + sidebar filtre; mobil `Sheet` drawer filtre.

### Homebrew Detail Mixed Auth

Published homebrew misafire açık — `useGetHomebrewQuery` public. DRAFT yalnızca sahip API'den görür; FE owner badge + edit link koşullu.

## Feature: Collections

`CollectionToggle` — heart/bookmark; optimistic toggle + rollback on error.

## Feature: Reference

Salt okunur — form yok. `ReferenceListPage` / `ReferenceDetailPage` public RTK query. Tip filtre `:type` path param enum shared'dan.

## Feature: Admin

`DataTable` + server-side cursor pagination. Row actions: deactivate, delete content — `ConfirmDialog` zorunlu. Admin API `adminApi` slice — tag `AdminUsers`, `AdminContent`.

Bulk işlem MVP dışı — tekil satır action.

